tt studenten f\u00e5 utsatt eksamen, sier han.", "Rektor Torbj\u00f8rn Digernes lover \u00e5 ta tak i saken.", "- Jeg beklager at familien n\u00e5 sitter med et inntrykk av at NTNU ikke reagerer som man skulle forvente i slike situasjoner, sier Digernes."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "student"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e0f3be5f053320ebe62d508bdf8a826d711bf97b7b3d200d6875c347c27175bf"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T09:50:21.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Da mormoren l\u00e5 for d\u00f8den hjemme i Kongsberg, ville Rasmus B\u00f8ckman ta eksamen ved den lokale h\u00f8gskolen. Men NTNU nektet ham \u00e5 flytte eksamen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1214460.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ntnu"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/6c9b8eda8f814e707231035860ae62c2441dfc8a.jpg?593acaf9"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Mormor for d\u00f8den - fikk ikke flytte eksamen -adressa.no", "\u00abVi gj\u00f8r ikke slik\u00bb", "M\u00e5tte dra fra d\u00f8dsyk mormor", "Sier unnskyld"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "6c9b8eda8f814e707231035860ae62c2441dfc8a"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "student"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["mormor", "eksamen", "flytte eksamen", "d\u00f8de"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["under dusken", "studenttinget", "h\u00f8gskolen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["buskerud", "kongsberg", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"f